CatDescriptText: Cutline of related article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 24, 1946, pg. 9 reads: " Pittsburgh Welcomes Nat'l Bridge Tournament - Hundreds Attend Sessions at Northside Elks, Kay Boys' Club - Approximately 300 bridge enthusiasts have gathered from all over the nation to vie...top honors in thirteenth annual conclave of  the American Bridge Association...held her under the sponsorship of the Keystone Bridge Club of Pittsburgh..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of man, and woman wearing contrasting plaid dress and ribbon inscribed "13th Annual Tournament American Bridge Association...," seated on wooden bench in interior with speckled floor
